title: Om Veg Cafe - Capitol Arcade
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Simple Indian food place inside a mall with some seating in the walkway. Has breakfast all day, vegan cakes, and an all-you-can-eat option that includes curry, rice, and naan. Similar to other Om restaurants but with a more extensive menu (with dosa, paratha, vegetable dishes, samosas, sweets). Items can be made vegan on request.
